<div class="section" style="background:#fefbf4">
  <div class="screen-wrapper">
    <div class="reviews screen" data-carousel-section="voice">
      <div class="reviews__bg-card reviews__bg-card--left"></div>
      <div class="reviews__bg-card reviews__bg-card--right"></div>
      <div class="reviews__slider">
        <div class="reviews__slider-prev slider-btn slider-btn--prev" data-carousel="voice"><svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="18" fill="#FF5100"/><path d="M20.5 12L15 17.5L20.5 23" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <div class="carousel-dots" data-carousel="voice"></div>
        <div class="reviews__slider-next slider-btn slider-btn--next" data-carousel="voice"><svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="18" fill="#FF5100"/><path d="M15.5 12L21 17.5L15.5 23" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
      </div>
      <div class="reviews__header">
        <div class="reviews__label">VOICE</div>
        <h1 class="reviews__title">多くの方に<br />ご好評いただいています</h1>
        <div class="reviews__subtitle">ペットラインしあわせマルシェより(PR)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="reviews__card main_01">
        <div class="reviews__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="reviews__card-body">
          <div class="reviews__card-content">
            <div class="reviews__card-heading">食べ残しなし！</div>
            <div class="reviews__card-divider"></div>
            <div class="reviews__card-text"><span>お試しフードを出したところ、クンクンと匂いを嗅いで「いつものと違う？」と確認しながら食べ始め、</span><span class="reviews__card-highlight">途中で休むことなく完食！</span><span>お腹がゆるくなることもなく、スムーズにフードの移行ができました。</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="reviews__card-author">ひろさん・7〜10歳</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reviews__card main_02">
        <div class="reviews__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="reviews__card-body">
          <div class="reviews__card-content">
            <div class="reviews__card-heading">トッピング不要に</div>
            <div class="reviews__card-divider"></div>
            <div class="reviews__card-text"><span>今までのご飯はふやかしたりトッピングしないと食べてくれませんでしたが、</span><span class="reviews__card-highlight">カリカリでもトッピングなしでも食べてくれた</span><span>ので嬉しいです。</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="reviews__card-author">さちさん・1〜7歳</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reviews__card main_03">
        <div class="reviews__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="reviews__card-body">
          <div class="reviews__card-content">
            <div class="reviews__card-heading">シニア犬にも</div>
            <div class="reviews__card-divider"></div>
            <div class="reviews__card-text"><span>15歳のパピヨンです。好き嫌いが多く、飽き性で同じフードが続くと食べてくれなくなります。こちらは</span><span class="reviews__card-highlight">小粒で食べやすい</span><span>みたいです。</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="reviews__card-author">パピヨンさん・15歳</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reviews__card main_04">
        <div class="reviews__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="reviews__card-body">
          <div class="reviews__card-content">
            <div class="reviews__card-heading">他ブランドから切替</div>
            <div class="reviews__card-divider"></div>
            <div class="reviews__card-text"><span>他のグレインフリーからの切り替えです。</span><span class="reviews__card-highlight">原材料や成分は同等以上。</span><span>この価格<span class="reviews__card-asterisk">※</span>では有り得ないよく出来たドッグフードだと思います。</span><span class="reviews__card-note">※お試し価格のこと。通常価格は店頭でご確認ください</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="reviews__card-author">yo3さん・1〜7歳</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img class="reviews__dog-image" src="/img/reviews-dog.webp" alt="" />
      <div class="reviews__disclaimer">※個人の感想です。効果には個体差があります。<br />※ご購入から約10日後のレビューになります。</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  /* ----------------------------------------
     Section & Screen Base
     ---------------------------------------- */
  .section {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
    height: 100dvh;
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding-bottom: 55px;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
  }

  .screen-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ----------------------------------------
     Reviews Container
     ---------------------------------------- */
  .reviews {
    position: relative;
    width: 440px !important;
    height: 959px !important;
    overflow: hidden !important;
    background-color: var(--background-02);
    will-change: transform;
  }

  /* ----------------------------------------
     Background Cards (decorative)
     ---------------------------------------- */
  .reviews__bg-card {
    position: absolute;
    top: 348px;
    width: 326px;
    height: 372px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 5px #0000000d;
  }

  .reviews__bg-card--left {
    left: calc(50% - 509px);
  }

  .reviews__bg-card--right {
    left: calc(50% + 188px);
  }

  /* ----------------------------------------
     Slider Controls
     ---------------------------------------- */
  .reviews__slider {
    position: absolute;
    top: 741px;
    left: 57px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: 326px;
  }

  .reviews__slider-prev,
  .reviews__slider-next {
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease;
  }

  .reviews__slider-prev:active,
  .reviews__slider-next:active {
    transform: scale(0.85);
  }

  /* ----------------------------------------
     Header
     ---------------------------------------- */
  .reviews__header {
    position: absolute;
    top: 101px;
    left: 42px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 9px;
    width: 357px;
  }

  .reviews__label {
    align-self: stretch;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-size: var(--font-size-s);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.70px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .reviews__title {
    width: 397px;
    margin-left: -20px;
    margin-right: -20px;
    color: var(--brown-title-text);
    font-size: 34px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.70px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .reviews__subtitle {
    align-self: stretch;
    color: #565656;
    font-size: var(--font-size-s);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.14px;
    line-height: 27px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ----------------------------------------
     Review Cards
     ---------------------------------------- */
  .reviews__card {
    position: absolute;
    top: 348px;
    left: 57px;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 326px;
    height: 372px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 5px #0000000d;
  }

  .reviews__stars {
    position: absolute;
    top: 25px;
    left: 25px;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-size: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .reviews__card-body {
    position: absolute;
    top: 54px;
    left: 25px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    width: 276px;
  }

  /* ----------------------------------------
     Card Content & Typography
     ---------------------------------------- */
  .reviews__card-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .reviews__card-heading {
    align-self: stretch;
    color: var(--black);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.20px;
    line-height: 44px;
  }

  .reviews__card-divider {
    align-self: stretch;
    width: 100%;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--orange);
  }

  .reviews__card-text {
    align-self: stretch;
    height: 206px;
    color: var(--black);
    font-size: var(--font-size-l);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.16px;
    line-height: 25px;
  }

  .reviews__card-text span {
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.03px;
  }

  .reviews__card-highlight {
    color: var(--orange) !important;
    font-weight: 700 !important;
  }

  .reviews__card-text .reviews__card-asterisk {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    vertical-align: sub;
    line-height: 0;
  }

  .reviews__card-text .reviews__card-note {
    display: block;
    color: #565656;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.12px;
    line-height: 18px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .reviews__card-author {
    align-self: stretch;
    color: #888888;
    font-size: var(--font-size-s);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.14px;
    line-height: 27px;
  }

  /* ----------------------------------------
     Dog Image & Disclaimer
     ---------------------------------------- */
  .reviews__dog-image {
    position: absolute;
    top: 269px;
    left: calc(50% - 75px);
    width: 150px;
    height: 83px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .reviews__disclaimer {
    position: absolute;
    top: 787px;
    left: calc(50% - 129px);
    color: #565656;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.12px;
    line-height: 18px;
  }
</style>
